The '''1957<U+2013>58 [[Liga Bet]] season''' saw [[Hapoel Tiberias F.C.|Hapoel Tiberias]] and [[Hapoel Ramla F.C.|Hapoel Ramla]] win their respective regional divisions. However, there was no promotion to [[Liga Alef]] or relegation to [[Liga Gimel]], after the [[Israel Football Association]] decided to abandon the league before the end of the season, due to suspicions of bribery.<ref name="All the league matches starting this Saturday were abandoned due to the fixed matches">[http://archive.football.org.il/multimedia/PDF/Newspapers/hadashot/1958/05-14-1958.pdf All the league matches starting this Saturday were abandoned due to the fixed matches (Page 1)] Hadshot HaSport, 14 May 1958, archive.football.co.il {{he icon}}</ref>

